za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui

Class SamplePoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui.SamplePoint

  • public class SamplePoint
extends java.lang.Object
    SamplePoint acts as a simple data storage device to allow for enhanced communication between the DataPanel and DataProcessor modules. Theoretically it cou- ld be extended to enhance calculations on both sides and determine variables such as rate through functional operators as apposed to functions
    See Also:
    DataPanel, DataProcessor
